{
  "stem": "15694.11",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, I hadn't heard my name for a long time because I was a number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I said, oy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said what I expected him to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Your father is dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, I remember one single tear-- that was all-- stole out of my eye.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Before it was down, halfway down, it was dried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I remember it because-- I remembered it so many times later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I will speak to it in a minute again, about that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Anyway, obviously, it came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I probably am alone now, but maybe father, mother, and sister are still alive somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because when you are there, you see living people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then you see maybe, well, I was alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Maybe they are as well, by some miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The next thing I remember, that was eight day-- eight days before the-- before my liberation, and 11 days before the war was declared officially at the end.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the-- that was one of the things that made me stop talking every time I started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that is also a reason why I had to write a book.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because beyond this point, I could never speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because previously, I have repeated it now so often, I had a lump in my throat and I couldn't go on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, the next thing I remember was that I found myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it must have been very nearby, in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And somebody says, they don't gas here or well, I'll say at least that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Now, I'm not sure if gassed there or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But at the time, when we arrived there, maybe they didn't gas anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I would say that most likely-- I'm not sure at that stage or definitely a few days later, the top elements of the camp had left already.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
